@page "/how-enigma-works"

<SeoHead Title="How Enigma Works | Puzzle Maze Gameplay Guide"
         Description="Understand run flow, puzzle interaction, rewards, map ownership, and how Enigma economy systems connect to daily play."
         OpenGraphType="article"
         SchemaType="Article"
         Keywords="how Enigma works, puzzle maze gameplay, Enigma guide, maze run rules" />

<div class="content seo-page-shell">
    <section class="panel seo-page-hero">
        <span class="profile-kicker">Guide</span>
        <h1>How Enigma Works</h1>
        <p>Each run starts with a generated or saved maze. From there, you move room to room, solve puzzle locks, collect rewards, and reach the finish room before the run is abandoned or completed.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel seo-page-section">
        <h2>Run Flow</h2>
        <h3>Start a Maze</h3>
        <p>Generate a new maze or load a saved map. Before entry, choose available items and launch the run.</p>
        <h3>Solve Rooms</h3>
        <p>Rooms use direct interactions and console overlays. Some puzzles resolve in-room, while others open through the console with the <code>E</code> key.</p>
        <h3>Finish or Lose</h3>
        <p>Runs are permanent. Leaving a real maze counts as a loss. Successful completion awards MN, progression, and potential map outcomes.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel seo-page-section">
        <h2>Rewards and Progress</h2>
        <h3>Maze Nuggets</h3>
        <p>Room rewards, completions, daily systems, and economy activity all contribute to your Maze Nuggets balance.</p>
        <h3>Saved Maps</h3>
        <p>Discoveries can become persistent maps with market value, owner history, ratings, and leaderboard relevance.</p>
        <h3>Analysis and Voting</h3>
        <p>Owned maps can be assigned to analysis for daily MN. Staked map count also contributes to council vote weighting.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel seo-page-section">
        <h2>Live Systems</h2>
        <h3>Real-Time Updates</h3>
        <p>Friend requests, invites, player status, and key economy and voting updates are surfaced through in-app notifications.</p>
        <h3>Economy Dashboard</h3>
        <p>The economy tab tracks circulating MN, map distribution, listings, analysis status, and activity trends.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel seo-page-section">
        <h2>FAQ</h2>
        <h3>What happens if I leave a maze?</h3>
        <p>Leaving a real run ends it permanently and records the run as lost.</p>
        <h3>Do all puzzles use the console?</h3>
        <p>No. Some puzzles are solved directly in the room with movement and interaction, while others use the console overlay.</p>
        <h3>Can I replay or trade saved maps?</h3>
        <p>Yes. Saved maps can be replayed, rated, listed, sold, or assigned to analysis if you own them.</p>
    </section>
</div>
